GO TO Nurses Section

      > Click on "Admissions & Discharges"
      
      
      
              > Click on the link "Admit a Patient"
              
              
              
                    >  Enter the Patient's name in the Search Box and Click SUBMIT.
                    
                    
                    
                      > Now select the specific patient you want.
                      
                      
                      
                              > Choose the latest attendance of that patient (The First one in the list)
                              
                              
                                  > Tick the Admit Checkbox and enter other details as required.
                                  
                                  
                                                                    
                                          > Click SAVE
